data.description: Beautiful 2 story home with 3 Bedrooms, 3 bathroom, 3 car garage with covered back patio. 2 bathrooms located downstairs, a bonus room with full bathroom upstairs. Formal dining room or office. Huge pantry in kitchen with center island, snack bar and full tile backsplash. Features newer casement windows, fresh paint, and new flooring throughout home. Newer roof approximately 1 year old. Located close to downtown and Tulsa International Airport in the gorgeous Osage Hills.
